[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]、[[英國|英國]]和[[智利|智利]]在南極的領土主張構成重疊，引起了領土爭端。2012年12月18日，英國[[外交及聯邦事務部|外交及聯邦事務部]]將一片尚未命名的土地命名為[[伊利沙伯女皇地|伊利沙伯女皇地]]，以作為[[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]][[钻禧|钻禧]]的貢品<ref name="Foreign & Commonwealth Office Press Release">{{cite web |title=The Foreign Secretary has announced that the southern part of British Antarctic Territory has been named Queen Elizabeth Land |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/queen-elizabeth-land |work=Foreign & Commonwealth Office |publisher=HM Government |accessdate=2012-12-22 |date=2012-12-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160627122226/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/queen-elizabeth-land |archivedate=2016-06-27 }}</ref>。2012年12月22日，阿根廷政府傳召英國駐阿根廷大使{{link-en|約翰·弗裏曼|John Freeman (diplomat)}}抗議該領土主張<ref name="BBC News: Argentine Protest Against Queen Elizabeth Land">{{cite web |title=Argentina angry after Antarctic territory named after Queen |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-20822582 |work=BBC News |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |accessdate=2012-12-22 |date=2012-12-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021161130/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-20822582 |archivedate=2014-10-21 }}</ref>。不過，{{link-en|阿根廷－英國關係|Argentina–United Kingdom relations|阿根廷和英國之間的關係}}早已因兩國對[[福克兰群岛|福克兰群岛]]的主權爭議而破裂，而且當時正值[[福克蘭戰爭|福克蘭戰爭]]三十周年。

[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]和[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]從英國獨立前，上述[[澳大利亞南極領地|澳大利亞的聲稱領土]]和[[罗斯属地|紐西蘭的聲稱領土]]均為英國的領土。[[英國|英國]]、[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]、[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]、[[法國|法國]]、[[挪威|挪威]]均互相認可對方的領土主張。目前，澳大利亞在南極洲的聲稱領土是當中面積最大的一幅。

其他《[[南極條約|南極條約]]》的成員國亦對南極洲的土地有興趣，但該條約並不允許这些国家在條約生效時提出領土主張。<ref name="peecug1">{{cite web|url=http://library.jid.org/en/mono38/nieto.htm|title=La Antartica|publisher=Library.jid.org|accessdate=2008-11-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007084832/http://library.jid.org/en/mono38/nieto.htm|archivedate=2008-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="peecug2">{{cite web |url=http://www.afese.com/img/revistas/revista40/laantartida.pdf |title=LA ANTÁRTIDA |format=pdf |accessdate=2011-07-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410080228/http://www.afese.com/img/revistas/revista40/laantartida.pdf |archivedate=2016-04-10 }}</ref>

* {{flag|Brazil}}指定了「[[巴西南极属地|有興趣的區域]]」，但這不是正式的領土聲請。<ref name="Morris1988">{{cite book|last=Morris|first=Michael|title=The Strait of Magellan|date=1988|publisher=Martinus Nijhoff Publishers|isbn=0-7923-0181-1|page=219|url=https://books.google.com/?id=vqZJLAOnj58C&pg=PA145&lpg=PA145&dq=brazil+antarctica+zone+of+interest#v=onepage&q=brazil%20antarctica%20zone%20of%20interest&f=false |accessdate=2010-10-21|quote=... Brazil has even designated a zone of Antarctic interest that overlaps the Argentine sector but not the Chilean one ...}}</ref>
