| journal =Geophysical Research Letters|date=2008|volume=35|issue=18|page=L18602
|doi=10.1029/2008GL034939|bibcode=2008GeoRL..3518602T}}</ref>。南极半岛对于海平面的净影响更有可能是幅度更大的大气变暖所導致的<ref>
{{cite journal|language=en
|last1=Pritchard|first1=H.|coauthor=et al.
|title=Widespread acceleration of tidewater glaciers on the Antarctic Peninsula
|journal=Journal of Geophysical Research|date=2007|volume=112|issue=F3
|doi=10.1029/2006JF000597|bibcode=2007JGRF..11203S29P }}</ref>。

